description.en:
InfinityCake - Where holders of earn $CAKE tokens by holding $InfinityCake. 

InfinityCake uses storytelling to capture crypto-lovers and ethusiasts into learning more about staking and farming crypto. 

Through the usage of community voting and involvement through DAO we will enable InfinityCake to be a community powered coin.

The community are encouraged to share the best APYs farming pools on pancakeswap, allowing everyone in the community to gain. Incentives on sharing farming and staking strategies will be rewarded by the community. 

The crowdsourcing of knowledge of farming pools will allow all members of InfinityCake to practice extensive due diligence and research before crypto is staked in any farming pools on pancakeswap or the BSC Network.
